PermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/china-starts-second-day-war-games-around-taiwan-2024-05-24/</guid></item><item><title>中国驻英国大使馆表示，中方敦促英方停止无端指责</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/uk/china-urges-uk-stop-making-groundless-accusations-says-chinese-embassy-uk-2024-05-23/</link><description>中国驻英国大使馆发言人周五发表声明，呼吁伦敦方面停止对中国的无端指责，停止在乌克兰问题上火上浇油。</description><pubDate>Thu, 23 May 2024 23:56:09 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/uk/china-urges-uk-stop-making-groundless-accusations-says-chinese-embassy-uk-2024-05-23/</guid></item><item><title>解读：中国最新的房地产市场支持计划——其内容和利害关系</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/chinas-latest-property-market-support-package-its-contents-whats-stake-2024-05-23/</link><description>中国上周宣布了“历史性”措施，以稳定受危机打击的房地产行业，旨在清理库存并提振购房者需求。</description><pubDate>Thu, 23 May 2024 23:05:32 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china/chinas-latest-property-market-support-package-its-contents-whats-stake-2024-05-23/</guid></item><item><title>早盘竞价：市场降温，日本通胀即将来临</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/global-markets-view-asia-graphic-pix-2024-05-23/</link><description>展望未来一天的亚洲市场。</description><pubDate>Thu, 23 May 2024 21:47:10 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/global-markets-view-asia-graphic-pix-2024-05-23/</guid></item><item><title>巴西和中国呼吁与俄罗斯和乌克兰两国进行和谈</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/brazil-china-call-russia-ukraine-peace-talks-with-both-countries-2024-05-23/</link><description>路透社周四看到的一份文件显示，巴西和中国周四签署了一份联合声明，呼吁两国参与就俄罗斯和乌克兰之间的冲突进行和平谈判。</description><pubDate>Thu, 23 May 2024 20:11:15 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/brazil-china-call-russia-ukraine-peace-talks-with-both-countries-2024-05-23/</guid></item><item><title>赫斯-雪佛龙合并投票似乎已经成熟，以微弱优势获得通过</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/deals/hess-chevron-merger-vote-appears-ripe-narrow-approval-2024-05-23/</link><description>赫斯公司 (Hess Corp) 首席执行官约翰·赫斯 (John Hess) 必须在周二之前平息股东对其处理可能成为石油行业历史上最大的合并之一的抗议：拟议以 530 亿美元将这家石油生产商出售给雪佛龙公司 (Chevron Corp)。</description><pubDate>Thu, 23 May 2024 18:35:43 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/deals/hess-chevron-merger-vote-appears-ripe-narrow-approval-2024-05-23/</guid></item><item><title>美国、肯尼亚呼吁加大对发展中国家的支持</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/us-kenya-call-increased-support-developing-countries-2024-05-23/</link><description>美国总统乔·拜登和肯尼亚总统威廉·鲁托周四呼吁加大对肯尼亚等发展中国家的支持，包括通过中国等主要双边债权人减免债务。</description><pubDate>Thu, 23 May 2024 18:02:29 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/us-kenya-call-increased-support-developing-countries-2024-05-23/</guid></item><item><title>埃隆·马斯克现在表示，他反对美国对中国电动汽车征收关税</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/elon-musk-im-against-tax-incentives-evs-2024-05-23/</link><description>特斯拉创始人埃隆·马斯克周四在巴黎对科技投资者表示，他反对美国对中国电动汽车征收关税，这与他一月份警告需要采取贸易壁垒，否则中国将“摧毁世界上大多数其他汽车公司”的态度大相径庭。</description><pubDate>Thu, 23 May 2024 16:15:43 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/elon-musk-im-against-tax-incentives-evs-2024-05-23/</guid></item><item><title>由于交付仍然低迷，波音公司预计 2024 年将出现自由现金消耗</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/aerospace-defense/boeing-now-sees-negative-free-cash-flow-2024-deliveries-remain-sluggish-2024-05-23/</link><description>该公司财务主管周四表示，波音公司在 2024 年将烧钱而不是产生现金，第二季度的交付量也不会增加，因为这家美国飞机制造商正在努力应对一场导致其最畅销飞机产量减少的危机。</description><pubDate>Thu, 23 May 2024 15:45:56 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/aerospace-defense/boeing-now-sees-negative-free-cash-flow-2024-deliveries-remain-sluggish-2024-05-23/</guid></item><item><title>拜登和肯尼亚的鲁托承诺保护非洲及其他地区的民主</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/biden-welcomes-kenyas-ruto-white-house-with-investments-promises-2024-05-23/</link><description>美国总统乔·拜登周四欢迎肯尼亚总统威廉·鲁托到白宫进行国事访问，并承诺与非洲最强大民主国家之一的领导人在技术、安全和债务减免方面建立新的伙伴关系。</description><pubDate>Thu, 23 May 2024 14:13:05 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/biden-welcomes-kenyas-ruto-white-house-with-investments-promises-2024-05-23/</guid></item><item><title>中国阿里巴巴将通过发行可转换票据筹集 45 亿美元资金</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/retail-consumer/chinas-alibaba-raise-45-bln-through-convertible-notes-offering-2024-05-23/</link><description>阿里巴巴集团周四表示，将出售 45 亿美元的可转换优先票据，并计划用部分收益回购美国存托股票。</description><pubDate>Thu, 23 May 2024 13:43:13 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/retail-consumer/chinas-alibaba-raise-45-bln-through-convertible-notes-offering-2024-05-23/</guid></item><item><title>宫一专注，水手队瞄准亚洲冠军联赛冠军</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/sports/soccer/miyaichi-focused-marinos-set-sights-asian-champions-league-crown-2024-05-23/</link><description>横滨水手队边锋宫市亮相信日本队能够在周六的亚洲冠军联赛决赛第二回合中保持专注，击败东道主艾因队，夺得洲际冠军。</description><pubDate>Thu, 23 May 2024 13:24:28 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/sports/soccer/miyaichi-focused-marinos-set-sights-asian-champions-league-crown-2024-05-23/</guid></item></channel></rss>